[Amit Varma]: Wise words and while you were speaking, I got the title for our episode, Abhijit Bhaduri

04:16:17.360 --> 04:16:21.240
[Amit Varma]: breaks the algorithm, which kind of sums up, you know, and it's great advice to young people

04:16:21.240 --> 04:16:22.760
[Amit Varma]: also break the algorithm.

04:16:22.760 --> 04:16:27.360
[Amit Varma]: So boss, thank you so much for your generosity of being so patient, sharing your insights.

04:16:27.360 --> 04:16:29.680
[Amit Varma]: I've, I've had a great time.

04:16:29.680 --> 04:16:30.760
[Guest]: Thank you so much for having me.

